00091         namespace detail

00093                 template<class From>
00094                 struct enum_maker
00095                 {
00096                         explicit enum_maker(From& from): from_(from) {}
00097 
00098                         From& operator[](const value& val)
00099                         {
00100                                 from_.add_static_constant(val.name_, val.val_);
00101                                 return from_;
00102                         }
00103                         
00104                         From& operator[](const value_vector& values)
00105                         {
00106                                 for (value_vector::const_iterator i = values.begin(); i != values.end(); ++i)
00107                                 {
00108                                         from_.add_static_constant(i->name_, i->val_);
00109                                 }
00110 
00111                                 return from_;
00112                         }
00113 
00114                         From& from_;
